gdom general election in Ireland|1832]] }}\n{{s-aft |after=[[Frederick Mullins]] |after2=Charles O'Connell }}\n{{s-bef |before=[[Sir Frederick Shaw, 3rd Baronet]] |before2=[[Henry Chetwynd-Talbot, 18th Earl of Shrewsbury|Viscount Ingestre]] }}\n{{s-ttl |title=Member of Parliament for [[Dublin City (UK Parliament constituency)|Dublin City]] |with=[[Edward Southwell Ruthven]] |years=[[1832 United Kingdom general election in Ireland|1832]]\u2013[[1835 United Kingdom general election in Ireland|1835]] }}\n{{s-aft |after=[[George Alexander Hamilton]] |after2=[[John Beattie West]] }}\n{{s-bef |before=[[Richard Sullivan (MP)|Richard Sullivan]] }}\n{{s-ttl |title=Member of Parliament for [[Kilkenny City (UK Parliament constituency)|Kilkenny City]] |years=[[1836 Kilkenny City by-election|1836]]\u2013[[1837 United Kingdom general election|1837]] }}\n{{s-aft |after=[[Joseph Hume]] }}\n{{s-bef |before=[[George Alexander Hamilton]] |before2=[[John Beattie West]] }}\n{{s-ttl |title=Member of Parliament for [[Dublin City (UK Parliament constituency)|Dublin City]] |with=[[Robert Hutton (politician)|Robert Hutton]] |years=[[1837 United Kingdom general election|1837]]\u2013[[1841 United Kingdom general election|1841]] }}\n{{s-aft |after=[[John Beattie West]] |after2=[[Sir Edward Grogan, 1st Baronet|Edward Grogan]] }}\n{{s-bef |before=[[Garrett Standish Barry]] |before2=[[Edmond Roche, 1st Baron Fermoy|Edmund Burke Roche]] }}\n{{s-ttl |title=Member of Parliament for [[Cork County (UK Parliament constituency)|Cork County]] |with=[[Edmond Roche, 1st Baron Fermoy|Edmund Burke Roche]] |years=[[1841 United Kingdom general election|1841]]\u20131847 }}\n{{s-aft |after=[[Maurice Power]] |after2=[[Edmond Roche, 1st Baron Fermoy|Edmund Burke Roche]] }}\n{{s-civ}}\n{{s-bef |before=Sir John Kingston James }}\n{{s-ttl |title=[[Lord Mayor of Dublin]] |years=1841\u20131842 }}\n{{s-aft |after=George Roe }}\n{{s-end}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Oconnell, Daniel}}\n[[Category:1775 births]]